title: ICalloutVariable.UserReadableVariableName
description: Gets the name of the hole callout variable as it appears in the Dimension PropertyManager page in the Callout value drop-down list box.
returns: Name of the hole callout variable as it appears in the Dimension PropertyManager page in Callout value drop-down list box
remarks:
Call
ICalloutVariable::VariableName
to get the name of the hole callout variable as it appears in the Dimension PropertyManager page in the
Dimension Text
box.
